inson are more alike than you think</span></a></strong><span>and</span><strong><a href=\"https://almostcooperstown.substack.com/p/kyle-schwarber-has-a-long-way-to?utm_source=post-email-title&amp;publication_id=1216321&amp;post_id=204649445&amp;utm_campaign=email-post-title&amp;isFreemail=false&amp;r=gwh9&amp;triedRedirect=true&amp;utm_medium=email\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Kyle Schwarber has a long way to go to be a Hall of Famer</a></strong><span>by </span> </p></li>\n<li><p><strong><span>⚾ </span><a href=\"https://baseballreplayjournal.substack.com/p/banning-the-dh?utm_source=post-email-title&amp;publication_id=1265175&amp;post_id=204425146&amp;utm_campaign=email-post-title&amp;isFreemail=true&amp;r=gwh9&amp;triedRedirect=true&amp;utm_medium=email\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><span>Banning The DH: The movement that failed</span></a></strong><span>and </span><strong><a href=\"https://baseballreplayjournal.substack.com/p/the-dark-side-of-interleague-play?utm_source=post-email-title&amp;publication_id=1265175&amp;post_id=204102962&amp;utm_campaign=email-post-title&amp;isFreemail=true&amp;r=gwh9&amp;triedRedirect=true&amp;utm_medium=email\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">The Dark Side Of Interleague Play: Did we lose more than we gained?</a> </strong><span>by </span> </p></li>\n<li>\n<p>🏀 <strong><a href=\"https://www.houseofstrauss.com/p/jaylen-brown-is-the-new-nbas-first\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Jaylen Brown Is the New NBA’s First True Casualty</a></strong> by  </p>\n<ul><li><p><strong>Related:</strong> Listen to two of my absolute favorites, Ethan + Justin Termine, <a href=\"https://www.houseofstrauss.com/p/justin-termine-on-hot-nba-topics\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">talk about the crazy hoops offseason</a>.</p></li></ul>\n</li>\n<li><p><span>🏀 </span><strong><a href=\"https://www.basketballpoetry.com/p/the-13-most-and-least-consistent-9f1?utm_source=post-email-title&